            <!-- Register -->
            <h2 id="register-to-vote">Register to vote</h2>
            <p>There is no better way to find out how to register to vote in your state than using the official website run by the US government, <a href="https://vote.gov/" alt="" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vote.gov</a>. Voting is important for more than just Presidential elections - true change comes from participation in local elections.</p>
